                <h2 class="text-center" style="font-family: 'Public Sans', sans-serif!important;">WHO WE ARE</h2>
            </br>
                <div class="underlinetext" style="width: 10%;border-radius: 10px; border: 3px solid #aaa; margin: auto;"></div>
                <br></br>

            <p style= "font-size: 18px; font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif; text-align: justify;color:#555; letter-spacing: 1px;"><i class="fa fa-quote-left" style="font-size: 25px;" aria-hidden="true"></i> Intellify is the education initiative set up under SOLVE, established by the students &amp; alumni of IIT Delhi to “solve” the problems plaguing the Indian Education System. It envisions to create a platform where every student can showcase their talent, assess their skills and receive specific guidance on various ways to enhance their skills.

            Since its inception in 2017, Intellify has reached out to more than 100 cities, impacting 30,000+ students and 800+ teachers directly through its program and workshops. In its journey, it has worked with Delhi Government, NITI Aayog, MHRD (DIC), CBSE, Teach for India, CLI-IIT Gandhinagar and Design Department of IIT Delhi to organise programmes. <i class="fa fa-quote-right" style="font-size: 25px;" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </p>
